    9 Weapons will be affected by this 
    
    Sawbar, Hellfire, Infection, Madhouse, carnage,longbow, heartbreaker and blockhead
    
    Sawbar: Shoots E-tech Splatgun bullets, and got an increase elemental effect chance and damage.
    
    Hellfire: Makes mini fire nova shield explosions, got the aquamarine skin and a new barrel.
    
    Infection: Got the same effect as hellfire, but more stable and more status effect damage.
    
    Madhouse: Got  tinderbox, little evie, teapot and pocket spalsh damage, But this effect only happens when hitting an enemy. (I think slag Madhouse is better than other variants) 
    
    Carnage: Change the rockets to E-tech Splatgun Bullets. (Maybe a little bit lame)
    
    Longbow: Got an increase to elemental effect chance and got a 2 bullets/arrows more (they are extremely precise)
    
    Heart breaker: got  an increase in Elemental effect chance heartbreaker and got a the gemstone skin for tediore SG
    Blockhead: got  an increase in Elemental effect chance and Blockhead got a change to its barrel (Just cosmetic)
